  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The CT ratio of liver/spleen</measure>
    <time_frame>12 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>CT imaging has been used to assess hepatic steatosis and has been validated in relation to liver biopsy .The ratio of liver to spleen (L/S ratio) for CT attenuation values is an index, with a L/S ratio&lt;1 considered to represent fatty liver .</description>
  </primary_outcome>
